<plot>Poland was the first victim of Hitler's infamous blitzkrieg. Combat cameramen filmed the aerial campaign, showing preparations for flight, massive air strikes, and the appalling devastation wreaked upon Polish towns and armies. 'Norbert Schultze (I)' (qv)'s original score lyrically enhances this Nazi propaganda vehicle.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?193206</url></doc>
